import React from 'react'
import { Menu, Icon } from 'antd'
import styled from 'styled-components'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

const StyledMenu = styled.div`
  width: 100%;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
`

const StyledApp = styled.div``

export default ({ children }) => {
  return (
    <StyledApp>
      <StyledMenu>
        <Menu>
          <Link to="/search">
            <Menu.Item key="mail">
              <Icon type="mail" />
              Search
            </Menu.Item>
          </Link>
        </Menu>
        <Menu>
          <Menu.Item key="mail">
            <Icon type="mail" />
            Navigation One
          </Menu.Item>
        </Menu>
      </StyledMenu>
      {children}
    </StyledApp>
  )
}
